# Design Approved
**Approved at**: 2026-01-17
**User said**: "yes approved"

## Backend API Status - COMPLETE

### Endpoints Ready
| Endpoint | Method | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `/api/sidebar/config` | GET | Returns sidebar config for current user's firm |
| `/api/sidebar/config/:firmType` | GET | Preview config for specific firm type |
| `/api/sidebar/configurations` | GET | All configs (admin only) |
| `/api/sidebar/recommend` | GET | Recommended firm type based on employee count |
| `/api/sidebar/module/:moduleId/available` | GET | Check if module is available |
| `/api/sidebar/firm-type` | PATCH | Update firm type (owner/admin) |

### Market Module Control
```javascript
// Firm model has:
moduleSettings: {
  marketEnabled: Boolean  // default: false
}

// To enable Market for a firm:
PATCH /api/firms/:id
{ "moduleSettings.marketEnabled": true }
```

## Answers to Open Questions
| Question | Answer |
|----------|--------|
| Market module separate setting? | Yes - controlled by `firm.moduleSettings.marketEnabled` |
| Support pinning in Recents? | No - keep Recents auto-populated only (consider Favorites feature later) |
